Battle Tower Trainers

In the Battle Tower, enemy Trainers - their Trainer class and name - are pulled from a pre-existing list of Trainers. Every Trainer in this list has a number, a tier designation, and one or more Pokémon rosters associated with them. The tier designation determines whether the Trainer can be battled with those particular rosters in Singles or Doubles as well as Regular Class or Master Class. For Trainers found in the Regular Class, their tier also determines which sets of 7 battles the Trainer can be faced in. The roster that the Trainer will use is random. All Trainers' rosters are designed to have no two Pokémon of the same species or holding the same held item.

This page does not include data on Palmer or the Master Class Boss Trainers. Palmer's teams can be found on the Battle Tower page, and the Boss Trainers' teams can be found on the Boss Trainers page.
